            erat massa a et. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Lectus
            vehicula consectetur erat massa a et.
          </p>

          <!-- E-mail -->
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 p-6">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              ><path
                fill="#ec6b2f"
